name: DigiDaigaku Genesis Chibis
description: Dive into the captivating world of DigiDaigaku Genesis Chibis, our first-ever Bitcoin Ordinals collection! Embrace the delightful charm of these cute, Digi-inspired collectibles, each one a testament to creativity and innovation. With only 2022 in the collection, these exclusive Chibis are a groundbreaking venture into the world of Bitcoin Ordinals. And the best part? They're distributed for FREE amongst those who own a DigiDaigaku Genesis. Join us on our next journey with @DigiDaigaku Chibis, and become a part of the next frontier in collectible digital art!
